"or \"$\". It is wise to not suffix keywords with typical word separators, "
"such as:\n"
"\n"
"       ! ? . , : ; ) ] } / ' \" SPACE TAB LINEBREAK\n"
"\n"
"as those are needed to detect when to trigger keyword expansion."
